OL,3,CAfrica Oye returns as ticketed event
OL,4,Cfor the first time in its history
OL,6,FAfrica Oye, the UK's largest
OL,7,Fcelebration of African and Caribbean
OL,8,Fmusic and culture, is returning to
OL,9,FLiverpool's Sefton Park this June as a
OL,10,Fticketed event.
OL,12,FThe festival, which used to be a free
OL,13,Fevent, took a year off in 2025 with
OL,14,Forganisers saying it was due to rising
OL,15,Finfrastructure costs and new legal
OL,16,Frequirements mandating enhanced safety
OL,17,Fand security at public events.
