OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777399866
OL,3,CAfrica Oye returns as ticketed event
OL,4,Cfor the first time in its history
OL,6,FThe festival began in 1992 as a series
OL,7,Fof gigs in Liverpool city centre and
OL,8,Fhas grown into the one of the city's
OL,9,Fmost significant yearly events,
OL,10,Fattracting hundreds of thousands to
OL,11,FSefton Park since 2002.
OL,13,FAward-winning Afrobeats star
OL,14,FPatoranking, is set to make his
OL,15,FLiverpool debut, and there will also
OL,16,Fbe a performance from innovative
OL,17,FCongolese collective Fulu Miziki,
OL,18,Frenowned for their eco-friendly, Afro-
OL,19,Ffuturistic performances using self-
OL,20,Fmade instruments and costumes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
