OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1777399866
OL,3,CAfrica Oye returns as ticketed event
OL,4,Cfor the first time in its history
OL,6,FArtistic Director Paul Duhaney said:
OL,7,F"We're delighted to bring Africa Oye
OL,8,Fback to Liverpool this summer as a
OL,9,Fticketed event. Patoranking is a giant
OL,10,Fof Afrobeats, and Fulu Miziki's show
OL,11,Fwill be worth the wait.
OL,13,F"Both acts embody the creativity and
OL,14,Fdiversity at the heart of our
OL,15,Ffestival. The changes mean we can keep
OL,16,Fthe event safe and accessible for
OL,17,Feveryone."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@drryD@JO]
