OL,3,CAfrica Oye returns as ticketed event
OL,4,Cfor the first time in its history
OL,6,FOrganisers say they remain committed
OL,7,Fto keeping the festival affordable and
OL,8,Fwelcoming while meeting new safety
OL,9,Fstandards with tickets starting at #11
OL,10,Ffor Liverpool City Region residents.
